text: National Highway 730B, commonly referred to as NH 730B is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 30. NH-730B runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH730B connects Bareilly, Bhutah and Bisalpur in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Bareilly. : near Bisalpur : Terminal at Bisalpur. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 730B on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
